Description: ===================
        Doctr Versions Menu
        ===================
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/badge/goerz-doctr__versions__menu-blue.svg?logo=github
           :alt: Source code on Github
           :target: https://github.com/goerz/doctr_versions_menu
        
